{"tid":2174764,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"麻煩柒婆自已睇下華大基因的track record, 先叫市民去免費檢測","createTime":"2020-08-26T05:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T06:08:06.000Z","uid":268271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3c4d623f1ead283d06a205f03009ddafcd690de5","tid":2174764,"uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:53:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0D4o8c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0D4o8c4.jpg&h=481246fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/515505/%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC-%E8%8F%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0%E4%BE%9B%E7%91%9E%E5%85%B8%E8%A9%A6%E5%8A%91%E7%8F%BE3700%E5%81%87%E9%99%BD%E6%80%A7-%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F%E9%83%A8%E9%80%9A%E5%A0%B1%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F515505%2F%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AC-%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%25BA%25E5%259B%25A0%25E4%25BE%259B%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%2585%25B8%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E5%258A%2591%25E7%258F%25BE3700%25E5%2581%2587%25E9%2599%25BD%25E6%2580%25A7-%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2580%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25A1%259B&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDrXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=f6ad8dd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/515505/%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC-%E8%8F%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0%E4%BE%9B%E7%91%9E%E5%85%B8%E8%A9%A6%E5%8A%91%E7%8F%BE3700%E5%81%87%E9%99%BD%E6%80%A7-%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F%E9%83%A8%E9%80%9A%E5%A0%B1%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9B</a>"},{"pid":"7e2244d6224960566a4e223e6ee051dd0f47e9af","tid":2174764,"uid":268271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:54:38.000Z","msg":"路透社、《紐約時報》等多間外媒報道，瑞典公共衛生署（The Public Health Agency of Sweden, Folkh&auml;lsomyndigheten）25日公布，因一批在中國生產，來自華大基因的新冠肺炎核酸檢驗試劑有缺陷，導致約3,700名使用該試劑的人士出現假陽性，誤變確診患者。<br />\n無法區分出極少量的病毒和陰性<br />\n<br />\n瑞典公共衛生署指出，試劑在今年3月至8月分發給民眾在家使用，但試劑卻無法區分出極少量的病毒和陰性結果。當局發現事件後，聯絡相關的市民，並調整數據，現時瑞典約有8.6萬宗新冠肺炎的確診個案，死亡個案為5,814宗。<br />\n<br />\n不過，當局則未有透露，全國共使用了多少個華大基因提供的試劑。署方要已將華大基因要改善及調整試劑，並就今次事件通報瑞典醫療產品局、歐盟，及世衞。<br />\n<br />\n據華大基因介紹，涉事的試劑獲中國、歐洲、美國、日本、澳洲、加拿大等國家使用，也列入世衞緊急使用的採購名單，目前已經向全球180多個國家和地區分發。《香港01》就事件向華大基因查詢，暫未獲回覆。"},{"pid":"2c000bf946ede90c6936fbe660a9ba083b856278","tid":2174764,"uid":90601,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:56:18.000Z","msg":"本身想去 但怕驗錯 現在不去了"},{"pid":"189f52c4e05974e7fa4efecc63e56a261f5cc61d","tid":2174764,"uid":268271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2c000bf946ede90c6936fbe660a9ba083b856278","tid":2174764,"uid":90601,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:56:18.000Z","msg":"本身想去 但怕驗錯 現在不去了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T06:00:02.000Z","msg":"之後幫你打大６疫苗<br />\n大６疫苗track record正到大６喱都喊打"},{"pid":"af3eb03a7ee8154fd77b9384277333e010388027","tid":2174764,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T06:00:14.000Z","msg":"柒婆就一定知<br />\n<br />\n係所謂專家唔講啫"},{"pid":"a35692a82f25c3f8f3a2034ed7fa704f518193b7","tid":2174764,"uid":53027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T06:01:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ou1653r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOu1653r.png&h=a095e8e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7ad3834927d3205d6344b3d28b86c7dc4ce58bd","tid":2174764,"uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af3eb03a7ee8154fd77b9384277333e010388027","tid":2174764,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T06:00:14.000Z","msg":"柒婆就一定知<br />\n<br />\n係所謂專家唔講啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T06:07:08.000Z","msg":"中午Cable news有報, 好波"},{"pid":"82e53